  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  defaultText: Damn bro, you didn't have to take a shark-sized bite out of the mood!
    I'm just here tryna have some fun man! I guess lets just make these sandwiches
    and get on with our lives then...
